title: BTS continues their streak on 'Billboard 200'!!
excerpt: BTS continues their streak on 'Billboard 200'! Their album 'Love Yourself: Tear' ranked 84th on the charts this week, making it their 13th consecutive week on the chart! In addition to the 13-week streak, 'Love Yourself: Tear' also ranked #1 on 'World Albums', #5 on 'Independent Albums', #25 on 'Top Album Sales', and #73 on 'Canadian Albums'. They're also currently setting the record for 'Longest Consecutive Streak at #1' on 'Social 50'!
